title: Rocket launchers found on outskirts of Ludhiana | india-news | Hindustan Times
text:
Rocket launchers found on outskirts of Ludhiana india Updated: Feb 13, 2017 20:18 IST PTI Ludhiana At least 25 rocket launchers were found at an empty plot near Dehlon town on the Malerkotla-Ludhiana road near here.(ANI Photo) 
At least 25 rocket launchers were found at an empty plot near Dehlon town on the Malerkotla-Ludhiana road near here. 
Deputy Commissioner of Police (DCP) Bhupinder Singh said the rocket launchers were in the form of scrap. 
“The entire area has been cordoned off and bomb disposal squad has been summoned,” he said. 
Police are investigating.
